cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper is about natural language generation for task-oriented dialog using neural generation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of neural generation for training conversational agents, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for generating responses, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks for training models, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the evaluation of the models, which falls under the category of cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
